                        <p>
                            I extend my warm greetings on behalf of IIITDM Kancheepuram. IIITDM Kancheepuram is an Institute of National Importance established by the Ministry of Education with a vision to develop a premier Institute of Excellence in IT, Design, and Manufacturing.
                            <br/><br/>
                            IIITDM Kancheepuram aims to create an academic environment that fosters innovation, entrepreneurship, and research excellence, with a strong industry-academia interface. We follow a robust "learning by doing" practice under which the Institute strives to provide its students with state-of-the-art facilities, industry exposure, and hands-on experience in cutting-edge technologies, preparing them to become leaders in their chosen fields.
                            <br/><br/>
                            
                            IIITDM Kancheepuram offers various UG, PG, and Ph.D. programs, such as B.Tech in CSE, ECE, ME, and SM, and M.Tech in CSE, ECE, ME, and SM, and M.Des. in Integrated Product Design. Additionally, IIITDM Kancheepuram offers various workshops, frequent conferences, and industry interactions for professionals and working individuals in different fields not only allowing them to exchange ideas but also stimulating research.
                            <br/><br/>
                            
                            IIITDM Kancheepuram has signed several MoUs with various organizations and Institutes to facilitate collaborative research, student exchange programs, and other activities. The strong faculty base that graduated from top technical institutes engages and guides the students in R&D activities to make them innovative and future thinkers. Many of our faculty are experienced practitioners who have a penchant for interactive classroom sessions, ensuring that the content is on par with prevalent industry demands. Overall, the students are groomed in a conducive environment and I am sure they are industry-ready and productive from day one. I wish the upcoming placement program a great success and look forward to establishing relationships with new recruiters while also strengthening the current partnerships. I welcome you once again to realize your experience with IIITDM Kancheepuram.
